snippet.textDisplay:
Must've heard this song a number of times from 2015 when I first heard it during a advertising conclave. 

This song makes me see through the relationship of my loved ones with their fathers. Be that of my sisters who are all too emotional and close to my dad to my youngest neice whose dad pampers her the most and to my wifes dad who spoilt her much before her before our wedding. 

Everyone had their best phase of life with their dads where my Neice who's about 8 is loving the warmth shes getting from her dad. My wife on the other hand, had her good old days with her dad but isnt in talking terms with her dad anymore. Can feel her pain through this song and can feel how my father in law would've been missing her. I've tried my best to get them together but have failed a number of times. 


My sisters who are all married have a lovely relationship. They usually call him up every single day.

Me as a youngest child have nothing but gratitude for being able to live and love my mom and dad ❤️

I've started hugging my parents early morning and can't tell you how good the day gets later. 

May all beings be happy. 🙏
